  "id": "RAW_f56e09fa",
  "title": "前 OpenAI 研究员跨界做文创：Ilya 发型帽子走红，AI 成潮牌！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652636000&idx=3&sn=b846a2fb15853231fd2ad140e3ca921b",
